              "loglevel": "INFO",
              "data_body": "{\"traceId\":\"453460-10.226.84.58-1223-1782787491351-1859\",\"extParam\":{\"robotWeworkId\":\"31331584\",\"leaseHost\":\"http://app-center-huiju-private-domain-lease.ke.com\",\"houseId\":\"107115941238\",\"contactInfo\":\"{\\\"address\\\":\\\"松陵镇亨通路396号优橙家20幢2405\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"赵燕豪\\\",\\\"phone\\\":\\\"130****5753\\\"}\",\"cityCode\":\"320500\",\"groupId\":\"10796992492521987\",\"aiRobotUcId\":1000000031335865,\"msgId\":\"1052154\",\"datacenterHost\":\"http://app-center-huiju-cloudkeeper-datacenter.ke.com\",\"latestMsgId\":\"1052154\",\"ruleHost\":\"http://rule.cloudkeeper.huiju.ke.com\",\"msgTime\":1782787490000,\"senderType\":5,\"aiRobotUserId\":\"31335865\",\"triggerSource\":10,\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2606268164\",\"atList\":\"\"},\"cityCode\":\"320500\",\"groupId\":\"10796992492521987\",\"className\":\"com.ke.huiju.cloudkeeper.support.vo.fact.ServiceKeeperFact\",\"isConfident\":\"0\",\"sessionId\":\"new_session_id:SERVICE_KEEPER--GROUP_CHAT--10796992492521987--4#1782787490000\",\"aiInvolve\":\"0\",\"businessScene\":1,\"firstTrigger\":1,\"requestId\":\"1052154\",\"senderType\":5,\"serviceId\":\"private-domain-lease\",\"triggerSource\":10,\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2606268164\",\"sessionInitiator\":5,\"matchingPlan\":\"GENERAL\",\"isInfoComplete\":\"0\",\"messageContent\":\"亲爱的租客小伙伴🥳\n欢迎入驻贝壳省心租的温馨小窝🏠，今天可是个超棒的日子，房子正式交付给您啦！\n--------------------------------\n当您完成缴费后，系统会把门锁的初始密码发送到您签约时留的手机号上，您可得留意查收哦～\n--------------------------------\n🔐修改密码：打开贝壳找房APP，用签约手机号登录→依次点击【我的】进入【租约】→【智能门锁】→【密码管理】→输入新密码，原密码自动失效。（要是没收到短信发的密码，就得瞅瞅是不是费用还没交完哦~） \n--------------------------------\n🔔以后若是没有按时缴纳租金，系统将会自动冻结门锁密码哦，不过别担心，缴费后半小时就会自动解冻～\n--------------------------------\n📌更多门锁常见问题，可点击这里：#小程序://贝壳找房丨二手房新房租房装修/门锁问题指引/vTpTJ23cPvIirig\n\n愿每一次暖灯长明，照亮您奔赴理想的漫漫征途哇✨！\"}",
